---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy"
  description="What this site does and does not collect. No login, no registration, no tracking — and your safety comes first."
>
  <header class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="page-header__eyebrow">About</p>
      <h1>Privacy</h1>
      <p class="page-header__lead">
        Looking for information about gambling can feel sensitive. This site is
        built so you can do that freely and privately.
      </p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container prose">
      <h2>No account, no registration</h2>
      <p>
        Everything here is free and open. There is no login, no sign-up, no
        membership, and no fee to read anything or download any resource. You do
        not give us your name, email, or any personal information to use the site.
      </p>

      <h2>What we collect</h2>
      <p>
        This is a static website. It does not ask for or store personal
        information about you, and it does not use advertising or advertising
        trackers. If we add basic, privacy-respecting traffic measurement in the
        future, we will describe it here first — it would count visits without
        identifying individuals.
      </p>

      <h2>Links to other organizations</h2>
      <p>
        When you call or text a helpline, or follow a link to another organization
        (such as a state council, a treatment directory, or 988), you leave this
        site and that organization's own privacy practices apply. Helpline privacy
        policies vary by call center; we do not make promises on their behalf.
      </p>

      <h2>Your safety</h2>
      <p>
        If you share a device and want to browse privately, your browser's private
        or incognito mode will keep this site out of your history. To leave quickly,
        you can close the tab at any time — nothing here requires you to be signed
        in.
      </p>

      <h2>Questions</h2>
      <p>
        If you have a question about privacy on this site, please
        <a href="/about">contact us</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
